HEADWORD: Fu
<hw>Fu</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Chin.]</ety> <def>A
department in China comprising several <part>hsein</part>; also, the
chief city of a department; -- often forming the last part of a name;
<as>as, Paoting-<ex>fu</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

